We are hiring developers, Go developers.

810
00:45:58,515 --> 00:46:01,155
And then you can, there's
links, you can find me.

811
00:46:01,456 --> 00:46:03,315
Feel free to connect with me on LinkedIn.

812
00:46:03,815 --> 00:46:04,606
Thank you for listening.

